nodes.text: New Kisge was the eighth moon of Chaasch in Suolriep sector, with dense underbrush-covered wilderness. It was the Samuac homeworld. General Vanden Willard established Delta Base on the moon prior to the Battle of Yavin. Being remote, the moon escaped the attention of the Empire.
It has been noted that instances of "Sulorine" as included in Secrets of the Sisar Run were misspellings of Suolriep.
